Package: surveyexplorer
Title: Quickly Explore Complex Survey Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Liam", "Haller", , "haller@dezim-institut.de", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-8033-6599"))
Description: Visualize and tabulate single-choice, multiple-choice, matrix-style questions in survey data.
    Users can group cross-tabulations, frequency distributions, and plots by categorical variables and integrate survey 
    weights for complex designs. Ideal for quickly uncovering descriptive patterns in survey datasets.
